    "asOf": "2025-12-17",
    "date": "2026-05-13T21:49:44Z",
    "text": "Fiscal Year 2025 Veterans Affairs Major Medical Facility Authorization Act\n\nThis bill authorizes the Department of Veterans Affairs to carry out a major medical facility project in St. Louis, Missouri, during FY2026.\n\nThe bill specifies the maximum amount that may be spent on the project and details that the project consists of the construction of a new bed tower, clinical building expansion, consolidated administrative building and warehouse, utility plant, and parking garages."
  },
